data.description: Gen Digital, Inc. engages in the provision of security, storage, and systems management solutions. The company is headquartered in Tempe, Arizona and currently employs 3,500 full-time employees.  The firm offers a range of cyber safety brands, including Norton, Avast, LifeLock, MoneyLion, Avira, AVG and CCleaner, among others. Its cyber safety portfolio provides protection across three categories in multiple channels and geographies, including security and performance, identity protection, and online privacy. The company also offers solutions in digital identity and access management, digital reputation, and restoration support services. The company provides real-time protection for PCs, Macs and mobile devices against malware, viruses, adware, ransomware and other online threats. These offerings monitor and block unauthorized traffic from the Internet to the device to help protect private and sensitive information when customers are online. Its LifeLock, Avast and AVG brands include monitoring credit reports, the dark web and social media accounts to help safeguard its customers’ personal information. Its VPN solutions provide an encrypted data tunnel.
